summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the City Light Department, RELEASING EASEMENTS for an electric distribution line over that portion of the north half of the west half of the southwest quarter of the northeast quarter of Section 9, Township 23 North, Range 4, East, W.M. and the north 30 feet of that portion of the northeast quarter of the southwest quarter of the northeast quarter of Section 9, Township 23 North, Range 4 East, W.M., lying west of Peter Western Road, King County, Washington. (P.M. \#230409-1-002 (C) and (D))
